{"word":"G2470 - ἴσος - ísos - ee'-sos - + agree","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἴσος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ísos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ee'-sos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">+ agree</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சமமான, ஒவ்வும் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"equal, in quality, in quantity"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably from <a href=\"#/G1492 - εἴδω - eídō - i'-do/1492\">G1492</a> (through the idea of <i>seeming</i>); <i>similar</i> (in amount or kind): - + agree, as much, equal, like.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2470/2470\">G2470</a>, <a href=\"#/G2471/2471\">G2471</a>, <a href=\"#/G2472/2472\">G2472</a>"}]}